summary: An ordinance authorizing the City Comptroller to see, and the City Treasurer to accept, redemption of certificates of delinquency issued upon lots seven (7), eight (8), Nine (9), Ten (10), Eleven (11), Twelve (12), Thirteen (13), Fifteen (15), Sixteen (16), Seventeen (17), Block Two (2), Eureka Addition, to the City of Seattle, under Ordinance No. 23038, upon payment of the sum herein specified and in the manner herein provided.
